Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野兽爆发 跳吧 飞吧 冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你为什么要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么盯着人家看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比刚才更快了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才他喝的药里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,含有什么特殊的成分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厉害的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一动起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…就有种怪怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来我似乎睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实根本就没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是…忍者的精髓所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯老师 我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又中计了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你以为我在这里就能睡大觉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是单纯喝醉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就毫无痛苦地送你到那个世界去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查克拉不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤得这么重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果继续呆在水里会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么砍不到他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易痛痛快快地睡上一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋真够吵的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是很厉害吗 过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的动作…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如您所知 所谓醉拳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝得越多 醉得越厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拳法的威力就越强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前在饭馆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当小李把酒和水搞混后喝了一丁点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和宁次两人联手 才勉强制服了李
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人没能制服他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他是敌人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然能制服他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是总不能让这么可爱的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身受重伤啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过喝了小小一杯就醉成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他把整瓶酒都喝掉的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就无敌了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 他才刚出院不久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体到底能支撑多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用的是醉拳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是头一次见到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你不过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击方式依然是横冲直撞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无规律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且速度奇快无比
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青春热血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不出他的行动规律
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能打到我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是厉害的体术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的攻击能力是骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的分身小鬼告诉过你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就让你醒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可…没喝醉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就让你清醒一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没醉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我还没成年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子是不可以喝酒的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的血继限界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快思考对策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定还有取胜之道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本跑不远嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 又追上来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋晕乎晕乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 这伤口…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来 我刚才似乎喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这副模样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你的酒醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的血继限界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血继…限界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的血继限界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以自由地操纵骨细胞和破骨细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至连钙的浓度 形成骨头的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人的身体里有两百多块骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:15:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言 骨头的数量并不固定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 骨头终究是骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折断它就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是人类的骨头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐松之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完蛋了 臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次是阿斯玛救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯玛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次出现危机被救的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不是100%啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能幻想有人来帮我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气味逐渐飘远了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的上衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎忽略了平日所熟悉的自身气味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是用它消除了自己的气味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很清楚气味的性质啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我没能察觉到你的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 兵分两路来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一手还真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才开始动真格的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是尽可能地拖住这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须避免可能导致自身毁灭的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不使用绝招根本不是他的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然刚做了手术 并不是最佳状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只开八门遁甲的第一门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一门 开门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表莲华
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用骨头抵消了这一脚的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度很快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么想 都没什么好对策
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑不下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你这只丧家之犬\N连嚷嚷的力气都没有了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死到临头还笑什么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们这一次是友军了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶的同盟国
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂之…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说砂之国与木叶重归旧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初我们并非自愿攻击木叶的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.45,0:22:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这次一样 只是完成任务罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.25,0:22:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你们不是三个人一起来的吗
